description:
Cubeverse - Deep Dive
is exclusively reserved for the winners of different twitter contests of the iota cubes twitter account. 

Only those who participate and are confirmed by the official IOTA Cubes Twitter account will have access to this project. 

Cubeverse - Deep Dive joins the cubes universe of IOTA Cubes and consists of a total of 10 different animations that reveal the transition from METACUBE to a previously undiscovered world.
name: CUBEVERSE - Deep Dive - Twitter Competition
